Drupal installation made easy. Process:
1. Downloads or detects drupal, unpacks it
2. Downloads libraries
3. Downloads modules (Needs improvement)
4. Setup installation profiles (Manual)

===============================================

18-May-2012, ver. 0.0.6
A. Drupal updates
- SEO Modules added: Google Analytics, Meta Tags, XML site map
- Module updates: Admin menu, features
B. Code updates:
- Installation complete
- - Take care of .htaccess, cookie issue
- - Copy & modify installation profile
- - Copy drupal & delete installation files

